 explaining what to do. Your benefit may be stopped if you don&rsquo;t go. </p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@money/documents/digitalasset/dg_195544.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Limited capability for work questionnaire' (PDF, 397KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Limited capability for work  questionnaire’ (PDF, 397KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.direct.gov.uk/prod_consum_dg/groups/dg_digitalassets/@dg/@en/@disabled/documents/digitalasset/dg_177366.pdf\" title=\"Download 'A guide to Employment and Support Allowance - the Work Capability Assessment' (PDF, 157KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘A guide to Employment and Support Allowance - the Work Capability Assessment’ (PDF, 157KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n"},{"web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/employment-support-allowance/how-to-claim","slug":"how-to-claim","order":4,"title":"How to claim","body":"<p>You can apply for Employment and Support Allowance: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>over the phone (or textphone) - an adviser will fill in the form for you</li>\n  <li>by post - send form ESA1 to your local <a href=\"/contact-jobcentre-plus\" title=\"Find your nearest Jobcentre Plus\">Jobcentre Plus office</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>Contact centre numbers</strong><br />\n<strong>Telephone:</strong> 0800 055 6688<br />\n<strong>Textphone:</strong> 0800 023 4888<br />\n<strong>Welsh language telephone:</strong> 0800 012 1888<br />\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 6pm</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>The interactive version of form ESA1 can be filled out on a computer.</p>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dwp.gov.uk/docs/esa1-print.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Form ESA1' (PDF, 600KB)\" rel=\"external\">Download ‘Form ESA1’ (PDF, 600KB)</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"form-download\">\n<p><a href=\"http://www.dwp.gov.uk/docs/esa1.pdf\" title=\"Download 'Form ESA1 - interactive' (PDF, 600KB)\" r